## ðŸŸ¦ 12. Shell Scripting Basics

### Shebang

```
#!/bin/bash
```

### Variables

```
name="DevOps"
echo $name
```

### Conditions

```
if [ $x -gt 10 ]; then
  echo "Greater"
fi
```

### Loops

```
for i in 1 2 3; do
 echo $i
done
```

### Functions

```
hello() {
 echo "Hello"
}
hello
```

